{"data":[{"name":"101:1","price":"1. (மரணித்தவர்களையும்) திடுக்கிடச் செய்யும் சம்பவம்!","arabic":"ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6158,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"101:2","price":"2. (அத்தகைய) திடுக்கிடச் செய்யும் சம்பவம் என்ன?","arabic":"مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6159,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"101:3","price":"3. (நபியே!) திடுக்கிடச் செய்யும் சம்பவம் இன்னதென்று நீர்அறிவீரா?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6160,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"101:4","price":"4. அந்நாளில் மனிதர்கள் சிதறிக்கிடக்கும் ஈசல்களைப் போல் ஆகிவிடுவார்கள்.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6161,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"101:5","price":"5. கொட்டப்பட்ட பஞ்சுகளைப்போல் மலைகள் ஆகிவிடும்.","arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6162,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"101:6","price":"6. எவருடைய (நன்மையின்) எடை கனத்ததோ,","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6163,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"101:7","price":"7. அவர் திருப்தியுள்ள வாழ்க்கையில் (சுகமாக) வாழ்ந்திருப்பார்.","arabic":"فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6164,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"101:8","price":"8. எவனுடைய (நன்மையின்) எடை இலேசாகி(ப் பாவ எடை கனத்து) விட்டதோ,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6165,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"101:9","price":"9. அவன் தங்குமிடம் ஹாவியாதான்.","arabic":"فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6166,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"101:10","price":"10. அந்த ஹாவியா இன்னதென்று (நபியே!) நீர் அறிவீரா?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهۡ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6167,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"101:11","price":"11. (அதுதான்) கனிந்து கொண்டிருக்கும் (நரக) நெருப்பாகும்.","arabic":"نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6168,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"}],"chapter":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah","Chapter Al-Qari'ah","Qari'ah","Surah Qari'ah","Chapter Qari'ah","Al Qari'ah","Surah Al Qari'ah","Chapter Al Qari'ah","Surah 101","Chapter 101","The Calamity","القارعة"]}